<template>
    <el-table
      stripe
      style="width:65% ;height: 650px;margin: -20px 0;" 
      :data="tableData"
      >
      <el-table-column
        prop=""
        label=""
        width="80">
        <template slot-scope="scope">
        <el-avatar shape="square" :size="50" :fit="fit" :src="url" style="margin: 0 10%;"></el-avatar>
      </template>
      </el-table-column>
      <el-table-column
        prop="name"
        label="昵称"
        width="80">
      </el-table-column>
      <el-table-column
        prop="id"
        label="账号id"
        width="120">
    </el-table-column>
    <el-table-column
        prop="fans"
        label="粉丝数"
        width="100">
    </el-table-column>
      <el-table-column
      fixed="right"
      label=""
      width="180">
      <template slot-scope="scope">
        <el-button type="primary" icon="el-icon-plus" circle></el-button>
  <el-button type="success" icon="el-icon-user-solid" circle></el-button>
  <el-button type="danger" icon="el-icon-close" circle></el-button>
      </template>
    </el-table-column>
    </el-table>
  </template>
  <script>
  import avatars from"./assets/avatars.png";
  export default {
    data() {
      return {
        url: avatars,
        tableData: [{
          name: '望闻问切',
          id:'2020214531',
          fans:'256'
          
        }
    ]
      }
    }
  }
</script>
